NAME
	m_save_object - save global variables in current object into a mapping

SYNOPSIS
	mapping m_save_object()

DESCRIPTION
	Saves all non static global variables of an object into a mapping
	that it then returns.  All variables are saved except those currently
	of the type object and function.

		variable_name	variable_value

		([ intvar:	number,
		   stringvar:	"stringvalue",
		   arrayvar:	({ variable_values }),
		   mappingvar:	([ index:value ]), ])

SEE ALSO
	m_restore_object

